step.  The same algorithm as Julia \code{BS3()} and MATLAB \code{ode23}.
\item \code{"ssp43"} -- Strong Stability-Preserving 4(3) pair, 4 stages.
Adaptive SSP method with a 3rd-order embedded error estimate.
